<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA4">
<l>ēṭu nilatti liṭuvataṉ muṉṉamvan teṅkaḷ kuḻāmpukuntu</l>
<l>kūṭu maṉamuṭai yīrkaḷ varampoḻi vantollaik kūṭumiṉō</l>
<l>nāṭu nakaramum naṉkaṟi yanamō nārāya ṇāyaveṉṟu</l>
<l>pāṭu maṉamuṭaip pattaruḷ ḷīrvantu pallāṇṭu kūṟumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before coming [to] him who places [his trust?] on the faulty ground, entering our family,</l>
<l>you who have a mind to join, forsaking [that] path, come, join [us] quickly!</l>
<l>You who are devotees having a mind to sing Nāmo Nārāyaṇāya</l>
<l>so that the region and the cities understand completely, come, proclaim many years!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
